verbose_text: Whereas SVP puncta distribution was greatly perturbed by loss of function of unc-104 / kinesin-3, as evidenced by loss of RAB-3 in the distal axon (XREF_FIG), ELKS-1 puncta distribution was largely unaffected in unc-104 / kinesin-3 mutants (XREF_FIG).
evidence: SVP puncta distribution was greatly perturbed by loss of function of unc-104/kinesin-3
